==Behind the scenes==
The Trials of Chiss families first appeared in [[Timothy Zahn]]'s [[2020]] novel ''[[Thrawn Ascendancy: Chaos Rising]]'', the first installment of ''[[Star Wars: The Ascendancy Trilogy]]''.<ref name="Chaos Rising" />

